    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''The Book's in Print, but Its Bibliography Lives in Cyberspace'' (front page, May 29): Why not publish the entire book on CD? That's the way the music industry is going.</p>
        <p>GEORGE A. ROBERTSON  Jefferson, Md., May 29, 2000</p>
      </block>
